                                    <p class="fz-18xr text-propercase fw-400 lh-24x dd-b-md-n">As heterosexual couples say - Rocco was not planned! He is our gift from the universe. At least to understand what love is! We do not know how he was born, what he suffered before he was saved. From the moment we met and decided that he was part of the family, we accepted our child as an equal member of the family with his needs. We do not have established rules and training, we do not believe in that. Rocco is a citizen and a full-fledged being with his own character and individuality.</p>
